---1 year---

One year na tayong naguusap bby!!! Omg!! Parang ang hirap paniwalaan! I've been the happiest, luckiest person on earth for more than a year already! And imagine, one year nakong nagsusulat ng letters for my bby! Oh ha! Sabi sayo consistent eh! MWAAA! Every day I've spent with you has been a gift and I'm really excited to spend more time with you this year! I know we'll make many more memories and I'm really excited and curious on how we'll grow as a couple this year! Ano anong nickname nanaman kaya ibibigay ko sayo HAHAHSHSH MWAAA ABABAYU BUNION!!

Belated happy new year!!! Happy monthsary!!! I love you so much!! More sleepy eepy pics this 2025!!!
